name: Master in Management Compass
tag_list: master-in-management, mba, mim, business-school, master-of-management, cems
overview:
The Master in Management Compass - also called MIM-Compass - is a platform for Management Masters. The key focus is on Masters in General Management and Business (MIM) but the site also includes specialized Management Masters such as the MSc in Finance or Marketing.

The MIM-Compass offers a database with descriptions of more than 1,000 programs and hundreds of business schools. In addition, users can find articles about the topic of Management Masters, for instance on the difference between the MBA and the Master in Management. Last but not least, the site provides an Ask-an-expert function, testimonials, information on rankings, and student blogs.
